Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:39.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(159,118.5)\fad(450,500)}第九幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:39.42,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(252,241.5)\fad(450,500)}全力暴擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是領主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是精靈啊 精靈 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:04.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你們也跟來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的公主殿下 獨佔真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也分給我們一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:20.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者們下一個目標應該是 加多爾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是把矮人族給解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但那裡是奧爾特最大的兵工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦很堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:38.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者可是捉摸不透的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:44.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡淪陷了的話 這個國家就徹底完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這批兵器也是要送上西方戰場的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:12.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我國的海上運輸艦隊好像全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有多少武器和防具都不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且上頭命令要增大基本產量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓矮人族們製造更多的裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再繼續壓榨他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會一個接一個地死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經有好幾個人都死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,礦山塌陷麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:55.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,廁所土間的泥土 歐派米的硫磺 木炭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,三樣東西一旦具備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,便能造黑色火藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火藥最大的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:20.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並非燒身的火焰 也不是飛濺的破片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:25.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊 給我扯大嗓門喊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人陷入恐慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加把勁沖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:43.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音和火光 衝擊和畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那和石火矢 棒火矢 還有火槍的道理是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:50.03,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：石火矢 棒火矢 種子島火槍，均是武器名稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是島津 種子島火槍的盛行之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很清楚這個道理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,衝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人 敵襲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是精靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是造反的那群傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這麼可怕的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在每天都在製作著這麼可怕的東西麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,小心地做喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然大家會一起上西天的 小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:33.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 沒問題 精靈的手很巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 盡情地射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是把火藥附在箭上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把棒火矢的用法借鑒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:48.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上与一和精靈的技術便可發揮出令人畏懼的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:52.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 連這裡都能聽到燒東西吵雜聲還真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的物資明明可以為我們所用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:59.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是浪費 啊 真是浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫吧 叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加劇恐慌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要爆炸了啊 火勢越來越大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊 到處都是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,會被殺光的 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:21.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要等他們恢復士氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 情況很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是城池 進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去拿下城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:59.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是奧爾特的大型兵工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:03.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們奧爾特黨 武裝親衛兵團鎮守的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會被你們這種反賊攻下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:19.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,重甲 大刀 長槍 無弓 無矢 無馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你們逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:23.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:31.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和廢城的那幫傢伙一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:39.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就可以發揮奧爾米擅長的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石棺之奧爾米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,單論石壁符術能力的話 她可是當世第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:56.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上 她是你們之中最有才能的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 一股老流氓的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:04.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是實際為83歲的老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,扔進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:15.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人崩潰了 這是好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好機會可值千金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,重裝兵全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…什麼啊 那個到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,門…把門關上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把門關上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把石壁那樣用麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用防禦術來把敵人趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:43.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像是一個為打倒敵人而生的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是城門關上的話還真是難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子 覆盆子好吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他要跟過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,癡呆的南蠻人有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,傳令 傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向奧爾米傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盆子 我要更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有了 老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有覆盆子的話 迦太基可是要毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對著這裡說話就可以了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個球是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米說對著講話就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 歐派 喂 聽到了麼 派歐米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,記住我的名字啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情怎麼都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石壁符還有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,按著我的指示做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一的弓術和你的符結合起來就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,城門正在關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個爆炸到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經放了狼煙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然距離援軍到達還有半日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們關上了城門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們應該就過不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把那些傢伙困於城外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:26.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,牆壁外駐紮地的士兵已經潰敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,城內之兵也只有少量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看我聯合援軍把他們包餃子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,牆壁上有階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信先生 好厲害啊 信先生 信先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 雖然石壁也非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這邊才真的強吧 無論怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要傳令兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:56.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 最好不過的就是傳令是即時的 沒有時間差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有注意到麼 術師們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是非常了不起的玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕這是思考角度的差別
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙應該想也沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:11.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只把這當做可以使研究和報告儘早傳達的便利的球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,使得分離的軍隊協調起來成為可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情他們從來都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮 實在幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,石壁也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米把那個作為防禦壁來使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而豐久把其當做投射器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後現在則是作為攻城的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:37.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作為外來技術的攜帶者的同時 也是思維的差異者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那些傢伙口中的廢棄物又到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為什麼要身處於這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又要我們做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這才是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是你們出現在那裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,個體差異使萬物蛻變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去擾亂一切吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抹消掉這個世界的「應有的樣子」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這個世界轉動吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1224,995.1)}Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:15.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城池 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐先生 我們去解放矮人族那幫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都是些強壯的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們精靈族從小就聽說很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈族的確很討厭矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:44.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都懷著恐懼與侮辱地聽父母訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:48.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那也包含著精靈族對自己沒有之物的羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的強壯身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的頑強意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們銳利的斧頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們應該就被囚禁在這個工坊都市內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:13:02.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,過去我們不敢想像精靈族和矮人族會有並肩作戰的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我們本來的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去解放他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:13.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族既鄙俗又暴力 鬍子亂糟糟的既骯髒又野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大口喝酒大口吃飯 又臭又可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用其粗壯的手臂碎石打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用其粗壯的雙腿踏在這片大地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,揮動大斧把敵人劈成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:32.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再回去邊豪飲邊笑著放聲高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是哪棟建築都是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,祇是名為工坊的監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族在我們精靈族投降了之後還在繼續反抗著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了農奴的我們的處境比他們要好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:57.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都一直在礦山或者工坊裡進行酷役吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:00.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想外面的騷動是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:08.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真諷刺 事到如今你們來解救我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:13.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「我們」 我們也是被拯救的一方 被漂流者們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論誰都可以 解放我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:23.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們受夠了 解放我們吧 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}只有勞動才是通向自由的路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:29.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了 即使你們是精靈族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:33.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,解放我們 老夫我們也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是矮人族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的鬍子真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:43.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,長得也不高 消瘦得很嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你就是那個「漂流者」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是他們擅自這樣稱呼我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥前就應該吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:57.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯吧 吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 歐派米 怎麼了 城市攻陷下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 歐派米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:16.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 豐久他貌似解放了矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:22.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族貌似都餓得不行 豐久就大喊吃飯吃飯這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:27.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非 莫非現在都在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還沒有攻陷下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,食料倉庫和我們帶過來的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還有煮剩下的食物都翻了個遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都扔到鍋裡開始煮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就在敵人的面前吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 馬 馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自把運貨的馬還有軍馬都宰來煮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙果然是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺爺 我把覆盆子都拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作為獎勵就把高盧賞賜給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}高盧：拉丁語Gallia，古代西歐地區名，法國、比利時等地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做成粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加多點熱水做成粥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會因為太餓導致消化不良而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:17.46,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,193.5)}在下猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:17.46,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(146.4,152.7)}大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以前猴子他說他就遭受過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,由於太餓了大口吃飯差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族死了就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:26.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別吵 聽好了 讓他們好好咀嚼再吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,森蘭丸 我也想吃泡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我不在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道啊蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:41.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好想吃米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,米飯是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,泡飯又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:55.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些煙是什麼 他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經解放了矮人族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們都在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在還不逃跑的話等我們吃完飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就會把你們全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走的人我是不會追殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把武器都丟掉空手逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快點做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在矮人族他們的眼中只有飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,離吃完飯已經沒有多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完飯下一個目標就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一副連你們的內臟都要吃掉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 這傢伙才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全知全能都為了戰鬥而特化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後通牒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打開城門還是去死 快決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第一大門已經被突破的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經沒有時間等待援軍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,兵長 等矮人族吃飽後就會攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被他們挖了地道 遲早也會攻陷這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會被全部殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者 你會放過我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打開城門的話就會讓我們逃走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是戰場的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不會砍手無寸鐵的降兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:38.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後地方官又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:43.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我把城門打開了 能放我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那你們開個小酒席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要給你準備切腹的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們都會等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,切 切腹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,介錯的話我會瞬間幫你解決
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.41,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}介錯： 為切腹自殺者斷頭（的人），為了減少他的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要切腹 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:01.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為城池淪陷了啊 城池守將切腹謝罪不是常識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,守將承擔責任這是義務 是榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑 說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 一定要切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會乖乖切下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,行 你沒有切腹的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有作為守將的氣度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有留下首級的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要去追擊他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過會放他們逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出爾反爾就前功盡廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為以前的壞毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以前總是讓我幹這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有人讓你幹那樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是「我們」的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一 追擊怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:31.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著符咒的空中偵查騎兵在到處飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:34.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒還有法術都不要用 會被偵查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這工作真難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也因為你們是十月機關 所以才接下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:44.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的冒險者公會的任務實在是太煩了 不想接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 多古
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是方便的望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:53.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是十月機關裡傳說中的「遺物」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,青銅龍 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是末席 但也是六大龍之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,它也加入黑王軍旗下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為青銅龍的加入所以停止向南進攻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你看一看「北壁」的南邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:21.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼 是我眼睛出問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是農田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物居然在耕地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怪物的文明化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物們開始進行原始的耕種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王那幫傢伙在那裡 在北壁那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:38.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正如大師傅大人所說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他和以往的廢棄物都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他並不是一心想要毀滅世界的廢棄物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想要取代人類成為怪物的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:12.04,difters-op,,0,0,0,,发动引擎 给我动力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:16.50,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油门 奏响福音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.21,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.21,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.98,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.90,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.40,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:40.57,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:42.95,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:45.41,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:51.25,difters-op,,0,0,0,,即使已超速 也无法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:56.00,difters-op,,0,0,0,,引擎全开 全身绷紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:56.75,difters-op,,0,0,0,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:56.75,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.27,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.69,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:17.11,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:19.98,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:22.53,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.91,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:04.14,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:04.14,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:08.40,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:08.40,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:13.36,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:13.36,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼热翻腾的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:20.49,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:20.49,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举心无旁骛的大义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:31.96,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:31.96,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:41.97,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:41.97,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.31,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.31,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:47.77,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:47.77,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:51.82,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:51.82,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:56.99,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:56.99,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.28,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.28,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:06.04,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:06.04,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与被染红的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:13.13,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:13.13,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲破无尽的今日 迈向新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:20.35,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:20.35,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌颂荣光 终归和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:24.47,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:24.47,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举更为雄壮的大义之旗
